    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being offered as a reliable, budget-friendly transportation option. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows its age with several noticeable issues. Expect some minor fluid leaks, a suspension that feels a bit loose, and interior wear including faded upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. The exterior has various scratches, small dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. While it starts up and drives reliably for daily commuting, it will eventually require some maintenance and minor repairs to keep it in optimal running order. It's a solid choice for someone who needs a functional car and doesn't mind a bit of character and DIY upkeep.",
