      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis remains structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's primary fatigue point. The high-revving powerplant benefits from a recently serviced VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and rotational reliability. Handling is sharp thanks to a refreshed multi-link rear suspension and M-tuned variable limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally tight. A purist\u2019s spec maintained for performance rather than preservation.",
